ZH: 这个机场有两条跑道。
EN: This airport has two runways.

ZH: 他半路上突然跑到了跑道上。
EN: He suddenly ran onto the runway midway.

ZH: 跑道上的飞机正在紧急起飞。
EN: The plane on the runway is taking off urgently.

ZH: 飞机驶向了跑道的尽头。
EN: The plane is heading towards the end of the runway.

ZH: 飞机成功降落在跑道上。
EN: The plane successfully landed on the runway.

ZH: 飞机滑行到了跑道的起点。
EN: The plane is taxiing to the starting point of the runway.

ZH: 跑道上有一些飞机正在排队等待起飞。
EN: There are some planes on the runway queuing for takeoff.

ZH: 跑道上的灯光非常明亮。
EN: The lights on the runway are very bright.

ZH: 警告！请勿横穿跑道。
EN: Warning! Do not cross the runway.

ZH: 空管员指挥着飞机进入跑道。
EN: The air traffic controller guides the plane onto the runway.

ZH: 这条跑道需要维修。
EN: This runway needs maintenance.

ZH: 雪天天气时，跑道会被除冰。
EN: The runway is de-iced during snowy weather.

ZH: 飞机在跑道上起飞后，扬起了一片灰尘。
EN: The plane took off on the runway, stirring up a cloud of dust.

ZH: 跑道上有飞机残骸散落一地。
EN: Plane wreckage is scattered on the runway.

ZH: 飞机刚刚落地，就靠在了跑道的一边。
EN: The plane landed and parked on one side of the runway.

ZH: 机场工作人员正在清扫跑道上的杂物。
EN: Airport staff are clearing debris from the runway.

ZH: 跑道上的飞机正等待检修人员进行维护。
EN: The plane on the runway is waiting for maintenance personnel.

ZH: 飞机在跑道上正加速前进。
EN: The plane is accelerating on the runway.

ZH: 跑道长了两公里。
EN: The runway is two kilometers long.

ZH: 这个机场的跑道非常宽阔。
EN: The runway at this airport is very wide.
